    <p class="lead mb-4">We are a small community of WoW players that maintains an open-source Wrath Of The Linch King private server powered by AzerothCore.</p>
    <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center mb-5">
      <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-success btn-lg px-4 me-sm-3">Create Account</a>
      <a href="/#how-to-play" type="button" class="btn btn btn-outline-info btn-lg px-4">How To Play</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="overflow-hidden" style="max-height: 30vh;">
    <div class="container px-5">
      <img src="/img/header-bg.png" class="img-fluid border rounded-3 shadow-lg mb-4" alt="Example image" loading="lazy" width="700" height="500">
