  </div>
</div>

<div class="row justify-content-md-center mt-4" id="how-to-play">

	<div class="col-md-8 px-4 py-5">
		<h2 class="pb-3 border-bottom text-center">How To Play</h2>

		<div class="row g-4 py-5">
      <div class="col-12 d-flex align-items-start">
        <div class="icon-square bg-light text-dark d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-3 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
          <i class="bi bi-person-plus"></i>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Create an Account</h2>
          <p>You need an account to access the Realm, <a href="/signup">click to create an account.</a> The account is used to log into both the game and our website.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-12 d-flex align-items-start">
        <div class="icon-square bg-light text-dark d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-3 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
          <i class="bi bi-cloud-arrow-down"></i>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Download the Game Client</h2>
          <p>You need a game client of version 3.3.5a, <a href="https://mega.nz/file/pd9lCBwK#SLzZZqLL6KSGxVHP8VuS_HLCF2R4cslZWUi1xs_fJ9I" target="_blank">click to download client from Mega</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-12 d-flex align-items-start">
        <div class="icon-square bg-light text-dark d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-3 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
          <i class="bi bi-menu-down"></i>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Already have a Client!</h2>
          <p>If you already have a client from elsewhere, make sure its version 3.3.5a then open the "World of Warcraft" folder and change the realmlist deleting all the text inside WoW/Data/enUS/realmlist.wtf replacing with: set realmlist logon.potadin.com</p>
        </div>
      </div>

			<div class="col-12 d-flex align-items-start">
        <div class="icon-square bg-light text-dark d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-3 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
          <i class="bi bi-journals"></i>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Note</h2>
          <p>Start the game using WoW.exe, not Launcher.exe. Login using your account name and password (do NOT login with email).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

	</div>
</div>